      "content": "i feel like there's nothing left of me. i sat in front of the canvas for six hours today and all i could see was just... emptiness. it's like the part of me that actually lived, the part that could see color and feel things, just evaporated. i'm just a walking, breathing shell now. just a hollow shape moving through a world that doesn't mean anything anymore.",
